       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. REVERSE-CONTROL-FLOW.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 FLAG PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01 COUNT PIC 9(4) VALUE 0000.
       01 LIMIT PIC 9(4) VALUE 0010.
       01 INDEX PIC 9(4) VALUE 0000.
       01 RESULT PIC 9(4) VALUE 0000.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
       IF NOT FLAG = 'Y'
           PERFORM UNTIL COUNT > LIMIT
               MOVE COUNT TO LIMIT
           END-PERFORM
       ELSE
           PERFORM VARYING INDEX FROM 0 BY 1 UNTIL INDEX >= LIMIT
               MOVE INDEX TO RESULT
           END-PERFORM
       END-IF
       STOP RUN.
NEXT.
       MOVE 'DONE' TO FLAG.
       STOP RUN.

